  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Substudy 1: includes new starting dialysis patients on peritoneal dialysis PD or
             haemodialysis HD

          -  Substudy 2: stabile haemodialysis patients and peritoneal dialysis patients. Patients
             will be matched for gender, time on dialysis, diabetes, renal function at the start of
             dialysis.

          -  Substudy 3: patients on CAPD (continuous ambulant PD) or CCPD (continuous cyclic PD).
      </textblock>
